{"id":133103,"type":6,"name":"Terminator Salvation","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/dd/3f/133103_g1a4G.jpg","rating":{"total":39,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":0,"5":7,"6":20,"7":10,"8":1,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.1},"summary":"《魔鬼終結者：未來救贖》（Terminator Salvation）（又名：殺威遜、威遜終結者），是部2009年美國科幻末日啟示戰爭電影，第四部《魔鬼終結者》系列電影，由麥可吉（McG）所執導，克里斯汀·貝爾飾演成年版的約翰·康納（John Connor），以及山姆·沃辛頓飾演人類與機器人的混種人馬可仕·萊特（Marcus Wright），安東·葉欽（Anton Yelchin）飾演首集英雄凱爾·瑞斯（Kyle Reese）的年輕版本。T-800型終結者則分別是由阿諾·史瓦辛格與羅蘭·奇金格（Roland Kickinger）的身體作電腦描繪。\r\n\r\n這部電影為本系列的續集，事件點設定在未來2018年，跳脫前三部曲系列的架構模式，劇情著重於審判日後人類與天網間的戰爭，環繞在機器人與人類角色間的定位，約翰·康納如何成為世界的救世主。\r\n\r\nvia wiki","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>终结者2018</li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/33363\">Christian Bale</a>、<a href=\"/person/43396\">Sam Worthington</a>、<a href=\"/person/34162\">Anton Yelchin</a>、Moon Bloodgood、Helena Bonham Carter</li><li><span>配角: </span><a href=\"/person/34251\">Linda Hamilton</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>终结者4：救世主</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>魔鬼終結者：未來救贖</li><li><span>集数: </span>1</li><li><span>开始: </span>2009-05-21</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>115m</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt0438488</li><li><span>导演: </span>McG</li><li><span>编剧: </span>John Brancato、Michael Ferris</li>","collection":{"wish":3,"collect":51,"on_hold":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"电影","count":12},{"name":"终结者","count":9},{"name":"科幻","count":9},{"name":"美国","count":6},{"name":"生化機械","count":5},{"name":"Terminator","count":5},{"name":"核戰","count":4},{"name":"2009","count":2},{"name":"movie","count":1},{"name":"Warner.Bros","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":526735,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/526735","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":43396,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4c/10/43396_prsn_GGJgK.jpg","name":"萨姆·沃辛顿","desc":"主演"},{"id":34162,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/38/dd/34162_prsn_7f5fP.jpg","name":"安东·叶利钦"